title: Monetary Donations by Country for the Relief Effort in Haiti, 1.20.2010
name: Monetary Donations by Country for the Relief Effort in Haiti, 1.20.2010
description:
This dataset shows the amount of money (in US Dollars) that has been given toward the relief effort from the earthquake destruction in Haiti during the month of January 2010 among various countries around the world. The data was published on 1.20.2010

The data comes from mappingworlds.com through their show feature. Follow the url link below to see the source page.
